      "en": {
        "Name": "VPO-136 \"Hunter's Regret\"",
        "ShortName": "136 HR",
        "Description": "Originally a Molot VPO-136 Vepr-KM civilian hunting carbine built on the AKM platform. Reliable, simple, and intended for hunting trips and sport shooting. That changed when the rifle passed through Tony's workshop. The civilian trigger group didn't last long — replaced, reworked, and tuned until the old hunting rifle started behaving like the military rifle it once resembled. Now running fully automatic, the Vepr-KM has traded patience for aggression. Tony likes to say it finally remembered what it was built from."
      }
